title: Select Window in Tmux
tags: tmux @zettel _method
roam-id: 6cafaa63-306e-425d-bb64-26c6d4e4aaf9
type: text/markdown

``` bash
tmux select-window -t session_name:window_name
# or
tmux select-window -t session_name:window_name_index
```

example:

``` bash
tmux select-window -t main:2
tmux select-window -t main:editor
```
